02:54.790 --> 03:01.240
Now these perks can be as small as a thank you note and they can be as large as maybe you know meeting

03:01.240 --> 03:08.320
the creators in person but essentially for these rewards people pledge various amounts and usually people

03:08.320 --> 03:10.460
are expecting to get a good deal.

03:10.480 --> 03:16.720
They're expecting to be the first person who gets to use this product so that they can show off to their

03:16.720 --> 03:21.610
friends and family about how they were first to use that particular product.

03:21.610 --> 03:27.690
We all know somebody who bought an iPhone when it was second generation and they go on about it.

03:27.700 --> 03:29.820
