03:40.900 --> 03:47.650
might fail you might run away with the money or of many many things can happen that will lead them to

03:47.740 --> 03:52.440
essentially having invested in something where they're not going to get anything back.

03:52.450 --> 03:57.910
Now that should really never occur because by the time that you're launching your campaign you should

03:57.910 --> 04:01.390
already have thought about how you're going to manufacture.

