05:50.410 --> 05:56.760
to put up a lot of capital for a lot of risk and a twist on this kind of lending type of crowdfunding

05:56.800 --> 06:00.810
platform are one where you're essentially investing in debt.

06:00.820 --> 06:10.300
So for example you know if a startup needs money to grow and you are buying up that debt then if they

06:10.300 --> 06:16.060
do raise the next round and they gain more and they get more funding or if they get sold and they pay

06:16.060 --> 06:20.890
off their debt and then you're getting an interest way over and beyond what you would get from you know

06:20.890 --> 06:24.490
just having your money stored in a bank.

06:24.520 --> 06:26.800
So Funding Circle and lend invest.

